ecdaa (0.10.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ Zane Beckwith ]
  * Set compiler flags (e.g. -std= and -Werror) as add_compile_options.

  [ David R. Bild ]
  * Separate benchmarks from tests
  * add 'ecdaa-' prefix to tests

  [ Zane Beckwith ]
  * Travis: Use prefixed `prepare-tpm2` utility.

  [ David R. Bild ]
  * readme: add release badge to readme

  [ Zane Beckwith ]
  * Tests: Don't terminate test macros with semicolon
  * Add editorconfig.org file
  * test: Support device-file TCTI for TPM
  * test: Update tpm_ZZZ-test for new TPM_Sign behavior
  * Update signature algorithm for TCG Errata v1.15
  * travis: Use new simulator mirror
  * Use length-checked version of AMCL deserialization when reading output from TPM.
  * Improve return codes from schnorr functions.
  * test: Add repetetive "fuzzing" schnorr tests.
  * Mod-reduce c_out in schnorr-TPM
  * tpm: Retry TPM_Sign if nonce isn't full-length.
  * Bump minor version number.

